## Summary
Notivize is a no-code platform for product engagement notifications that integrates with Amplitude for cohort syncing. The documentation outlines a two-part setup process requiring an API key from Notivize's settings and configuration in Amplitude Data's Catalog, followed by steps to export cohorts with customizable sync cadence.

